  "transcript": [
    {
      "turn": 1,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Priyansh, I hope your day has been good. Did you get a chance to try adding tomatoes to your moong dal yet?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Yes, I tried it yesterday. Tasted good, but I think I added too much salt. My family said it was okay, but they didn't say it was delicious. Maybe next time I will add less salt."
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "That sounds like a good experiment. Adding tomatoes is a nice touch. What will you cook next?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I think I will try making a chicken curry this weekend. It's a new recipe I found online. Maybe I can add some spices differently than usual. I want to improve my cooking skills."
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "\"Chicken curry sounds fun! Trying new spices is a great way to learn. What kind of spices will you use?\""
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "I think I will use more garam masala and maybe some turmeric. I read that they add flavor and color. Not sure if I will like it, but I will try. Maybe add some cream at the end for a rich taste. What do you think?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "That sounds like a great plan! Garam masala and turmeric do add nice flavor. Will you share it with your family?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Yes, I always cook for my family. My mom loves helping, but my younger brother says I cook too much. Ha! I want to make something special so they can taste the difference. Maybe I will take a photo and show you?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "That sounds fun! Sharing photos is a good idea — I’d love to see it. What part are you most excited to try?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The cream part, maybe. I’ve never added cream to curry before. It sounds rich, but I’m not sure how it will mix with the spices. Let’s see! If it works, I’ll show you. If not, I’ll try again. Chalta hai!"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "The cream part sounds exciting to try! It will add a nice touch if it works. Will you use fresh cream or something else?"
    }
  ],
